sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/SDK
    participant APIServer as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as CodeFlare Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as CodeFlare Controller
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>OAuth Proxy + Dashboard
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Router: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>APIServer: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    APIServer->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate RayCluster<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook->>APIServer: Return mutated/validated CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    APIServer->>KubeRay: Notify RayCluster created
    APIServer->>Controller: Notify RayCluster created
    Controller->>APIServer: Create CA Secret (mTLS)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>APIServer: Create TLS Secret<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>APIServer: Create OAuth Config Secret<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>APIServer: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>APIServer: Create Ingress/Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    KubeRay->>APIServer: Create Ray Head Pod<br/>with OAuth sidecar
    KubeRay->>APIServer: Create Ray Worker Pods

    Note over User,Router: Flow 2: Ray Dashboard Access

    User->>Router: HTTPS GET /dashboard<br/>443/TCP TLS1.2+
    Router->>RayHead: Forward (passthrough)<br/>8443/TCP TLS1.2+
    RayHead->>User: Redirect to OAuth Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    User->>RayHead: OAuth callback with token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    RayHead->>User: Dashboard page<br/>OAuth session cookie

    Note over User,Router: Flow 3: AppWrapper Scheduling

    User->>APIServer: POST AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    APIServer->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate AppWrapper<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>APIServer: Return mutated CR
    APIServer->>Controller: Notify AppWrapper created
    Controller->>APIServer: Create Kueue Workload CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Controller: Kueue schedules workload
    Controller->>APIServer: Create wrapped resources<br/>(RayCluster, etc.)
